    <item>
      <title>Need 2X Vitamin D and other micronutrients if eat 2X more calories</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/need-2x-vitamin-d-and-other-micronutrients-if-eat-2x-more-calories/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/need-2x-vitamin-d-and-other-micronutrients-if-eat-2x-more-calories/</guid>
      <description>&lt;nav id=&#34;TableOfContents&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#the-science-of-micronutrients-in-clinical-practice--report-on-the-espen-symposium&#34;&gt;The science of micronutrients in clinical practice – Report on the ESPEN symposium&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#note-most-farmers-and-vets-know-this-but-very-few-doctors&#34;&gt;Note: Most farmers and vets know this, but very few doctors&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/nav&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;the-science-of-micronutrients-in-clinical-practice--report-on-the-espen-symposium&#34;&gt;The science of micronutrients in clinical practice – Report on the ESPEN symposium&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;ESPEN ENDORSED RECOMMENDATION| VOL 43, # 1, P268-283, Jan 2024  &lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1016/j.clnu.2023.12.006&#34;&gt;https://doi.org/10.1016/j.clnu.2023.12.006&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/attachments/d3.mock.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;image&#34; width=&#34;400&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Background &amp;amp; aims&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The European Society for Clinical Nutrition and Metabolism published its first clinical guidelines for use of micronutrients (MNs) in 2022. A two-day web symposium was organized in November 2022 discussing how to apply the guidelines in clinical practice. The present paper reports the main findings of this symposium.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Supplements taken by the founder of VitaminDWiki</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/supplements-taken-by-the-founder-of-vitamindwiki/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/supplements-taken-by-the-founder-of-vitamindwiki/</guid>
      <description>&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/attachments/d3.mock.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;image&#34; width=&#34;800&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;nav id=&#34;TableOfContents&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#supplements-taken-daily-thru-once-a-week&#34;&gt;Supplements: taken daily thru once a week&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#receptor-and-activation&#34;&gt;Receptor and Activation&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;          &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#vitamindwiki---the-risk-of-span-stylecolorf0050-span-diseases-at-least-double-with-poor-vitamin-d-receptorcategoriesvitamin-d-receptor&#34;&gt;VitaminDWiki - The risk of &lt;span style=&#34;color:#F00;&#34;&gt;50+ &lt;/span&gt; diseases at least double with poor &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/categories/vitamin-d-receptor&#34;&gt;Vitamin D Receptor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#vitamindwiki---vitamin-d-receptorcategoriesvitamin-d-receptor-activation-can-be-increased-in-15-ways&#34;&gt;VitaminDWiki - &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/categories/vitamin-d-receptor&#34;&gt;Vitamin D Receptor&lt;/a&gt; activation can be increased in 15 ways&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/nav&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;supplements-taken-daily-thru-once-a-week&#34;&gt;Supplements: taken daily thru once a week&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;(Manufacturer - rarely important, typically popular on Amazon)&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Daily&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Magnesium  &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#06F;&#34;&gt;Co-Factor✻&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#F00;&#34;&gt;VDR activate✻&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;   400 mg in water&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;need &amp;gt;100 mg average daily MgCl (bulk crystal, disolved in water)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Omega-3  &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#06F;&#34;&gt;Co-Factor✻&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;  - tend to take it the in morning,  (Coromega - tastes great)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
